---
title: Cal Smart Spicy Coconut Turkey Curry with Spinach and Peppers
description: This Caribbean-style curry brings the heat! Turkey is flavoured with garlic, ginger, Indian spices and spicy curry paste, then cooled off with creamy coconut milk. Lime-spiked jasmine rice, peppers and spinach complete this soul-warming dinner!

